Here is a list of all documented files with brief descriptions:
 pruicss.hPruicss driver interface
 pruicss_drv.cThis file contains device abstraction layer APIs for the PRU Subsystem. There are APIs here to enable/disable the

PRU instance, Load program to PRU and Write to PRU memory.
